data.description: If you've been looking for a home that you can just move right into..THIS is it! This completely renovated and updated property has so much to love! The main floor features a large gorgeous kitchen with white cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. There is a dining room, and living room that flow seamlessly together thanks to the gorgeous hardwood floors. The main level also has a full bathroom with laundry! Heading upstairs we have matching carpet throughout the hall and three bedrooms. All bedrooms are well sized with closets. There is also a second full bathroom upstairs. Everything in this home has been done for you. All you have to do is unpack and enjoy!
